@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 120
skinparam ranksep 60
skinparam padding 15
skinparam defaultFontSize 13

actor "User" as AUser

rectangle "Traffic Camera Browser" {
  boundary "Camera Detail + Playback UI" as UI
  control "Playback Controller" as PC
  entity "Camera" as CameraEntity
  entity "PlaybackRequest" as PR
  entity "RecordingSegment" as RS
  entity "HistoryEntry" as HE
  entity "User" as UserEntity
}

AUser --> UI : choose time range
UI --> PC : playback request
PC --> CameraEntity : verify camera exists
PC --> PR : create playback request
PC --> RS : retrieve video segments
PC --> UI : stream playback video
PC --> UserEntity : identify user
PC --> HE : record view\n(PLAYBACK)

note bottom of UI
Users can view playback of any camera
from the past 72 hours through the platform.
end note
@enduml